{"tid":1725053,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家一定要記得第一次機場和你suck既事","createTime":"2019-11-15T15:40:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T16:47:06.000Z","uid":160998,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b89d132a1a314eca8bc777e8dfd02faba10b4f57","tid":1725053,"uid":160998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:40:57.000Z","msg":"就係散水撚啊屌你老母<br />\n唔洗半個鐘由機場爆人變到得返幾十個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全撚部狗上黎改幅圖就話機場停電又就黎出機場特警開真槍<br />\n<br />\n最後呢？？<br />\n<br />\n大家不割不分化但係大家如果貿然信散水論，其實同出賣手足有咩分別<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果人地講一句屌手足係岩既，咪聽囉，但係照樣不割蓆。特別係冷氣軍師無資格加把口話手足，你地可以比意見但係唔好叫人唔好再幫手足或者即刻散水</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n真係唔該大家睇清楚邊d有用邊d無用，唔係一有人屌就要屌埋一份就要走。<br />\n<br />\n最後真係希望大家可以唔好再中散水計同以後唔再幫計<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />諗清楚d人咁樣講有無違背一開始既原則"},{"pid":"d9596d1b616696eebbd04ddb9a87f8ba45186e05","tid":1725053,"uid":160998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:42:02.000Z","msg":"唔好再中散水計同以後唔再幫計<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ff5241f2b03275634c6c0c8a73976db6ab1da92","tid":1725053,"uid":160998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:42:12.000Z","msg":"推1/10"},{"pid":"9608d6f128c111e4f68f767b1c1b108d5beaf60a","tid":1725053,"uid":160998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:42:23.000Z","msg":"推2/10"},{"pid":"f787515d3e2b6cabba4fea97db113bc9523e66f2","tid":1725053,"uid":160998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:42:34.000Z","msg":"推3/10"},{"pid":"34d02ed1d01d3ad62fb57b51d12dd12739e7793b","tid":1725053,"uid":160998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:42:45.000Z","msg":"推4/10"},{"pid":